'''辉瑞－BioNTech 2019冠状病毒病疫苗'''<ref name="who-2021-01-08">{{cite news |title=关于使用被列入紧急使用列表的辉瑞–BioNTech  COVID-19疫苗BNT162b2的临时建议 |url=https://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/338484/WHO-2019-nCoV-vaccines-SAGE_recommendation-BNT162b2-2021.1-chi.pdf |accessdate=2021-04-06 |work=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]] |date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406090712/https://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/338484/WHO-2019-nCoV-vaccines-SAGE_recommendation-BNT162b2-2021.1-chi.pdf |archive-date=2021-04-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Pfizer–BioNTech COVID-19 vaccine}}，簡稱：'''輝瑞BNT疫苗'''、'''輝瑞疫苗'''、'''BNT疫苗'''<ref name="who-BNT162b2">{{cite web|title=哪些人群可以接种美国辉瑞制药有限公司与德国生物新技术公司联合研发的COVID-19疫苗（简称“辉瑞疫苗”）？|url=https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/feature-stories/detail/who-can-take-the-pfizer-biontech-covid-19--vaccine|accessdate=2021-01-27|dead-url=yes|website=[[世卫组织|世卫组织]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127044008/https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/feature-stories/detail/who-can-take-the-pfizer-biontech-covid-19--vaccine|archive-date=2021-01-27}}</ref>，代號：'''BNT162b2'''，[[商品名|商品名]]：'''{{lang|en|Comirnaty}}'''<ref name="who-2021-01-18"/>、'''復必泰'''，[[國際非專利藥品名稱|國際非專利藥品名稱]]：tozinameran<ref name="INN">{{cite journal |author=World Health Organization |title=International Nonproprietary Names for Pharmaceutical Substances (INN). Proposed INN: List 124 – COVID-19 (special edition) |journal=WHO Drug Information |date=2020 |volume=34 |issue=3 |page=666 |url=https://www.who.int/medicines/publications/druginformation/issues/WHO_DI_34-3_PL124-SpecialEdition.pdf |access-date=2020-11-23 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127075410/https://www.who.int/medicines/publications/druginformation/issues/WHO_DI_34-3_PL124-SpecialEdition.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>），是一種專門對抗[[严重急性呼吸系统综合征冠状病毒2|严重急性呼吸系统综合征冠状病毒2]]（SARS-CoV2）的[[2019冠状病毒病疫苗|2019冠状病毒病疫苗]]<ref name="who-2021-01-14">{{cite news |title=Background document on mRNA vaccine BNT162b2 (Pfizer-BioNTech) against COVID-19 |url=https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/background-document-on-mrna-vaccine-bnt162b2-(pfizer-biontech)-against-covid-19 |work=World Health Organization |date=2021-01-14 |accessdate=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511143645/https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/background-document-on-mrna-vaccine-bnt162b2-(pfizer-biontech)-against-covid-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為一種[[信使核糖核酸|信使核糖核酸]]（mRNA）疫苗<ref name="CDC_Pfizer-BioNTech">{{cite web |title=辉瑞-生物科技COVID-19疫苗概述和安全性 |url=https://chinese.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/vaccines/different-vaccines/Pfizer-BioNTech.html |publisher=美国卫生与公众服务部 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422171538/https://chinese.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/vaccines/different-vaccines/Pfizer-BioNTech.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由德國[[BioNTech|BioNTech]]及美國[[輝瑞|輝瑞]]合作開發<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=What you need to know about BioNTech — the European company behind Pfizer's Covid-19 vaccine|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/11/biontech-the-european-company-behind-pfizers-covid-19-vaccine.html|accessdate=2021-04-04|date=2020-11-11|last=Browne|first=Ryan|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304192058/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/11/biontech-the-european-company-behind-pfizers-covid-19-vaccine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nejm-2020-12-31">{{cite news |title=Safety and Efficacy of the BNT162b2 mRNA Covid-19 Vaccine |url=https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/nejmoa2034577 |accessdate=2021-04-13 |work=The New England Journal of Medicine |date=2020-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101021944/https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/nejmoa2034577 |archive-date=2021-01-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。輝瑞與BioNTech於2020年11月18日公佈疫苗在第三期臨床測試的有效率達到95%<ref name="ukgov12-2">{{cite press release |title=UK medicines regulator gives approval for first UK COVID-19 vaccine |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/uk-medicines-regulator-gives-approval-for-first-uk-covid-19-vaccine |publisher=Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency (MHRA) |access-date=2 December 2020 |date=2 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202101605/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/uk-medicines-regulator-gives-approval-for-first-uk-covid-19-vaccine |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="boseley">{{cite news |first1=Sarah |last1=Boseley |first2=Josh |last2=Halliday |title=UK approves Pfizer/BioNTech Covid vaccine for rollout next week |url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2020/dec/02/pfizer-biontech-covid-vaccine-wins-licence-for-use-in-the-uk |access-date=14 December 2020 |work=The Guardian |date=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202074938/https://www.theguardian.com/society/2020/dec/02/pfizer-biontech-covid-vaccine-wins-licence-for-use-in-the-uk |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨後於11月20日向[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美國食藥局]]（FDA）申請緊急授權使用許可<ref name="FDA PR 20201211">{{cite press release | title=FDA Takes Key Action in Fight Against COVID-19 By Issuing Emergency Use Authorization for First COVID-19 Vaccine | publisher=U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) | date=2020-12-11 | url=https://www.fda.gov/news-events/press-announcements/fda-takes-key-action-fight-against-covid-19-issuing-emergency-use-authorization-first-covid-19 | access-date=2020-12-11 | archive-date=2021-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131224810/https://www.fda.gov/news-events/press-announcements/fda-takes-key-action-fight-against-covid-19-issuing-emergency-use-authorization-first-covid-19 | dead-url=no }} {{PD-notice}}
</ref><ref name="輝瑞申請緊急使用">{{cite news |title=輝瑞公司向FDA申請新冠疫苗緊急使用授權 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B/20201120-%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%90%91fda%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A |accessdate=2021-02-27 |work=RFI |date=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121094127/https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B/20201120-%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%90%91fda%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A |dead-url=no }}</ref>，美國於12月11日宣布批准緊急使用BNT162b2疫苗<ref name="FDA-Pfizer-BioNTech">{{cite web |title=Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine |url=https://www.fda.gov/emergency-preparedness-and-response/coronavirus-disease-2019-covid-19/pfizer-biontech-covid-19-vaccine |website=www.fda.gov |publisher=Food and Drug Administration |access-date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114221304/https://www.fda.gov/emergency-preparedness-and-response/coronavirus-disease-2019-COVID-19/pfizer-biontech-COVID-19-vaccine |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="let19">{{Cite news|date=19 December 2020|title=Swissmedic autorise un premier vaccin contre le coronavirus|url=https://www.letemps.ch/suisse/swissmedic-autorise-un-premier-vaccin-contre-coronavirus|access-date=19 December 2020|publisher=Le Temps|language=fr|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110142727/https://www.letemps.ch/suisse/swissmedic-autorise-un-premier-vaccin-contre-coronavirus|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2020年12月31日成為[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]首款核准使用的預防2019冠状病毒病疫苗<ref name="who-2021-01-18">{{cite news |title=Comirnaty® 2019冠状病毒病信使核糖核酸疫苗（COMIRNATY®，COVID-19 mRNA Vaccine） |url=https://cdn.who.int/media/docs/default-source/immunization/covid-19/21040_chinese_vaccine-explainer_comirnaty-2.pdf?sfvrsn=271a9940_8 |accessdate=2021-04-02 |publisher=世界世卫组织 |date=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2021-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402082129/https://cdn.who.int/media/docs/default-source/immunization/covid-19/21040_chinese_vaccine-explainer_comirnaty-2.pdf?sfvrsn=271a9940_8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="世衛第一支緊急核准">{{cite news |title=告別2020 輝瑞疫苗獲得世衛第一支緊急核准 |url=https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2088068 |accessdate=2021-02-27 |work=中央廣播電台 |date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126162804/https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2088068 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。輝瑞與BioNTech在2021年4月1日發表跟進接種者6個月的研究報告<ref name="pfizer-2021-04-01">{{cite news |title=Pfizer and BioNTech Confirm High Efficacy and No Serious Safety Concerns Through Up to Six Months Following Second Dose in Updated Topline Analysis of Landmark COVID-19 Vaccine Study |url=https://www.pfizer.com/news/press-release/press-release-detail/pfizer-and-biontech-confirm-high-efficacy-and-no-serious |accessdate=2021-04-20 |publisher=Pfizer Inc. |date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417082319/https://www.pfizer.com/news/press-release/press-release-detail/pfizer-and-biontech-confirm-high-efficacy-and-no-serious |archive-date=2021-04-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在收集12,000名完成兩劑疫苗注射並超過6個月的人士的數據進行分析後，顯示疫苗在現實世界的有效率為91.3%<ref name="cidrap-2021-04-01">{{cite news |title=Pfizer COVID vaccine 91% effective for at least 6 months |url=https://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2021/04/pfizer-covid-vaccine-91-effective-least-6-months |accessdate=2021-04-20 |publisher=University of Minnesota |date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427230530/https://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2021/04/pfizer-covid-vaccine-91-effective-least-6-months |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且沒有出現嚴重副作用，而有效率在所有年齡、性別及種族都大致相同<ref name="hket-2021-04-02">{{cite news |title=【輝瑞疫苗】下調有效率至91% 可預防南非變種新冠病毒 |url=https://inews.hket.com/article/2924096/%E3%80%90%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E8%87%B391-%20%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92 |accessdate=2021-04-20 |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422090003/https://inews.hket.com/article/2924096/%E3%80%90%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E8%87%B391-%20%20%E5%8F%AF%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年8月23日，輝瑞疫苗通過數據審核獲美國食藥局（FDA）批准正式授權使用，可為美國16歲或以上的人士施打<ref>https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5117845</ref>。

BNT162b2疫苗是德國BioNTech與美國輝瑞製藥各投入一半開發經費的研發成果<ref name="healthgap-2021-03-31">{{cite news |title=Pfizer and BioNTech Profiteering Exposed – More than Enough is Enough |url=https://healthgap.org/pfizer-and-biontech-profiteering-exposed-more-than-enough-is-enough/ |accessdate=2021-04-19 |work=Health Global Access Project |date=2021-03-31 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331183408/https://healthgap.org/pfizer-and-biontech-profiteering-exposed-more-than-enough-is-enough/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在開發初期更由輝瑞承擔全部研發經費<ref name="DW_BioNTech">{{cite news|title=谁研发了BNT162新冠疫苗？|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%B0%81%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86bnt162%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97/a-55578952|accessdate=2020-11-13|agency=德国之声|date=2020-11-12|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109145650/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%B0%81%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%86bnt162%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97/a-55578952|dead-url=no}}</ref>，BioNTech則在疫苗上市後向輝瑞分期還款<ref name="pharmanewsintel-2020-04-22">{{cite web |title=Pfizer, BioNTech Team Up to Advance COVID-19 Vaccine Development |url=https://pharmanewsintel.com/news/pfizer-biontech-team-up-to-advance-covid-19-vaccine-development |publisher=PharmaNewsIntel |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415012643/https://pharmanewsintel.com/news/pfizer-biontech-team-up-to-advance-covid-19-vaccine-development |dead-url=no }}</ref>，BNT162b2疫苗於2020年12月成為首種研發成功並實用化的核糖核酸疫苗<ref name="nytimes-2021-03-22">{{cite news |author1=Jonathan Corum, Carl Zimmer |title=How the Pfizer-BioNTech Vaccine Works |url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/health/pfizer-biontech-covid-19-vaccine.html |accessdate=2021-04-14 |work=The New York Times |date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409191243/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/health/pfizer-biontech-covid-19-vaccine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[復星醫藥|復星醫藥]]於2020年3月投資1.35億美元（約合1.20億歐元）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://investors.biontech.de/news-releases/news-release-details/biontech-and-fosun-pharma-form-covid-19-vaccine-strategic |title=BioNTech and Fosun Pharma form COVID-19 Vaccine Strategic |access-date=2021-02-20 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422071105/https://investors.biontech.de/news-releases/news-release-details/biontech-and-fosun-pharma-form-covid-19-vaccine-strategic |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://investors.biontech.de/news-releases/news-release-details/pfizer-and-biontech-co-develop-potential-covid-19-vaccine |title=Pfizer and BioNTech co-develop potential COVID-19 Vaccine |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217151013/https://investors.biontech.de/news-releases/news-release-details/pfizer-and-biontech-co-develop-potential-covid-19-vaccine/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，從而成為BioNTech信使核糖核酸疫苗在[[兩岸三地|大中華地區]]的代理商<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://investors.biontech.de/node/7301/pdf |title=BioNTech Press Release 7301 |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2021-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123101038/https://investors.biontech.de/node/7301/pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite press|title=復星醫藥聯手全球領先mRNA療法企業BioNTech 啟動新冠疫苗戰略合作|url=https://www.fosunpharma.com/zh-tw/news/news-details-3801.html|date=2020-03-16|accessdate=2021-04-18|website=復星醫藥|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418144902/https://www.fosunpharma.com/zh-tw/news/news-details-3801.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並選取候選疫苗BNT162b1在中國大陸進行臨床試驗，以符合中華人民共和國藥監部門對引入外國藥品到中國大陸上市的要求，惟復星醫藥於2020年11月決定放棄候選疫苗BNT162b1的後續測試<ref name="sina-2020-11-10" /><ref name="qq-2021-04-01">{{cite news |title=引进mRNA新冠疫苗面临盈利压力 复星郭广昌呼吁股东理解 |url=https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20210401A0CD4A00 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |work=腾讯网 |date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414080450/https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20210401A0CD4A00 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，改為引進由BioNTech與輝瑞研發成功的BNT162b2疫苗到中國大陸市場<ref>{{Cite press|title=BioNTech與復星醫藥宣佈達成協議向中國供應mRNA新冠核酸疫苗|url=https://www.fosunpharma.com/zh-tw/news/news-details-3820.html|date=2020-12-16|accessdate=2021-04-18|website=復星醫藥|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418144907/https://www.fosunpharma.com/zh-tw/news/news-details-3820.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並將BNT162b2疫苗命名「復必泰」。但中华人民共和国官方媒体时常质疑這種疫苗的安全性<ref name="huanqiu-2020-12-04">{{cite news |title=唱衰中国疫苗，西方有什么算计 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/40xYAtUnd6C |accessdate=2021-04-14 |work=环球时报 |date=2020-12-04 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414143629/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/40xYAtUnd6C |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="163-2021-01-17" />，指有多名该疫苗的接种者在接种后死亡<ref name="cctv-2021-01-16">{{cite news |title=辉瑞疫苗频现接种者死亡事件，西方主流媒体为何集体沉默？ |url=https://news.cctv.com/2021/01/16/ARTI47ulT4NlyDk1WUeUvZCs210116.shtml |accessdate=2021-04-14 |work=央视网 |date=2021-01-16 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414082521/https://news.cctv.com/2021/01/16/ARTI47ulT4NlyDk1WUeUvZCs210116.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="中媒批西方淡化辉瑞疫苗危险" />，又稱核糖核酸疫苗的技術與中國滅活疫苗相比並不成熟<ref name="huanqiu-2020-12-24">{{cite news |title=无中国疫苗参战，全胜病毒很难 |url=https://opinion.huanqiu.com/article/41EHFL70eb1 |accessdate=2021-04-14 |work=环球时报 |date=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414143630/https://opinion.huanqiu.com/article/41EHFL70eb1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="qq-2021-02-19">{{cite news |title=注射辉瑞疫苗死亡900多例，现在又要拿4000名孕妇做试验 |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20210219/20210219A0DVU300.html |accessdate=2021-04-19 |work=腾讯网 |date=2021-02-19 |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419085047/https://new.qq.com/omn/20210219/20210219A0DVU300.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，且稱歐美國家因為疫情嚴重而要這種採用嶄新技術的疫苗倉促上市<ref name="huanqiu-2020-12-24" /><ref name="ifeng-2020-12-05">{{cite news |title=胡锡进：辉瑞疫苗尚不成熟仓促上阵，美国股市和疫情太需要它 |url=https://news.ifeng.com/c/824LY9KbKFU |accessdate=2021-04-14 |publisher=凤凰新媒体 |date=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414185338/https://news.ifeng.com/c/824LY9KbKFU |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

